<template>
  <footer>
    <el-button v-if="!hide[0]" :type="type[0]??'default'" @click="onClick('prev')">{{
      text[0]??"Voltar"
    }}</el-button>
    <el-button v-if="!hide[1]" :type="type[1]??'primary'" @click="onClick('next')">{{
      text[1]??"Avançar"
    }}</el-button>
  </footer>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  name: "FormFooter",
  props: {
    hide: {
      type: Array,
      default:() => [false,false],
    },
    type: {
      type: Array,
      default:() => ["default","primary"],
    },
    text: {
      type: Array,
      default:() => ["Voltar","Avançar"],
    },
  },
  methods: {
    onClick(dir) {
      this.$emit(`btn-click-${dir}`);
    },
  },
};
</script>
<style scoped>
footer {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
}
</style>
